Class ClassicModeStrategy

java.lang.Object
com.comp2042.logic.mode.ClassicModeStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
GameModeStrategy
public class ClassicModeStrategy extends Object implements GameModeStrategy
Strategy for Classic Tetris mode. Standard gameplay with no special win conditions.
